		{
			"name": "reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURyMllTd2NREAE",
			"relativePublishTimeDescription": "год назад",
			"rating": 5,
			"text": {
				"text": "I've been a patient of Dr. Uskokovic for the past four years, and I can't speak highly enough of her exceptional care and expertise. Every time I visit Montenegro from the USA, I make it a priority to schedule an appointment with her. She has been a trusted healthcare provider not only for me but for my entire family, and we all have had wonderful experiences under her care.\nDr. Uskokovic is incredibly knowledgeable, thorough, and compassionate. She always takes the time to listen to our concerns and provides thoughtful, personalized advice. Her clinic is well-equipped, and the staff is friendly and professional, making each visit comfortable and stress-free.\nI wholeheartedly recommend her to anyone seeking top-notch gynecological care. Her dedication to her patients' well-being is truly commendable, and I am grateful to have found such a wonderful doctor.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
			"originalText": {
				"text": "I've been a patient of Dr. Uskokovic for the past four years, and I can't speak highly enough of her exceptional care and expertise. Every time I visit Montenegro from the USA, I make it a priority to schedule an appointment with her. She has been a trusted healthcare provider not only for me but for my entire family, and we all have had wonderful experiences under her care.\nDr. Uskokovic is incredibly knowledgeable, thorough, and compassionate. She always takes the time to listen to our concerns and provides thoughtful, personalized advice. Her clinic is well-equipped, and the staff is friendly and professional, making each visit comfortable and stress-free.\nI wholeheartedly recommend her to anyone seeking top-notch gynecological care. Her dedication to her patients' well-being is truly commendable, and I am grateful to have found such a wonderful doctor.",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
